            <p>To the Divine Spirits [-] a homeborn slave of our emperor [---]</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Line 1: The deceased slave’s single name is missing; it is odd that it was inscribed in the same line as “<hi rend="italic">Dis Manibus</hi>.”
                      Line 2: All but the beginning of what is likely a slave name is missing. It is likely the name of the dedicator.
                   </p>
